PROMC to HEPEVN converter.
-----------------------

1) Get an example file:
   wget http://atlaswww.hep.anl.gov/asc/promc/download/Pythia8.promc

2) Setup ROOT and compile: "make"

3) Create ROOT file:
   ./promc2hepevn Pythia8.promc Pythia8.hepevt

General syntax:

./promc2hepevt <file.promc> <file.hepevt>


S.Chekanov (ANL)
March 2014
